summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2606, for the improvement of Brandon Street, Lucile Street, Findlay Street, Mead Street, Juneau Street, each from 42nd Avenue South to 46th Avenue South; and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues all in the City of Seattle, by planking the same, under Ordinance No. 30435 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
